The code folder contains the following scripts with their description:
Required libraries:
nltk
os
json
codecs
sklearn
pandas
numpy
pickle
Collections

1. processing_text_data.py
This script runs over mini_newsgroups folder that contains the data set and save them into a dataframe and then save it into a pickle file.

2. tokenizor.py
This script tokenizes the each row in the dataframe using nltk library then save it into a pickle file.

3. bow.py
Runs bag of words algorithm on tokens and save output to pickle

4. train_test_split.py
Split data into training and testing dataset

5. train.py
Runs neural network on training dataset and save model

6. testANDrunViz.py
Runs and output test accuracy and graph of neural network

